## transfer labels via cell barcodes
proj <- addCellColData(ArchRProj = proj, data = df_label$predictedGroup_Co,
    cells = rownames(df_label), name = "predictedGroup_Co", force = TRUE)
proj$predictedGroup_Co = gsub('/', '-', proj$predictedGroup_Co)
proj$predictedGroup_Co = gsub('\\+', '', proj$predictedGroup_Co)
proj$predictedGroup_Co = make.names(proj$predictedGroup_Co)

## subset to cells with integrated labels
idxPass <- which(!is.na(proj$predictedGroup_Co) &  
                 !proj$predictedGroup_Co %in% c('NA.', 'Schwann'))

cellsPass <- proj$cellNames[idxPass]
proj = proj[cellsPass, ]
